<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-5484] PDFRenderer does not render letters when converting page to image</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-5484</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m using &lt;tt&gt;PDFRenderer.renderImageWithDPI&lt;/tt&gt; to convert pages of the attached PDF to images. However, some of the characters disappear and look like blank spaces after converting the page to an image (please see attached image).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
