                            <comment id="17574544" author="tilman" created="Wed, 3 Aug 2022 06:52:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I looked at tt2, there the oslash is displayed in PDFDebugger. That&apos;s a bold font, that&apos;s the orange text in the middle that is displayed properly.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17574773" author="jira-bot" created="Wed, 3 Aug 2022 15:53:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1903211 from Tilman Hausherr in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/2.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
