                            <comment id="17574775" author="tilman" created="Wed, 3 Aug 2022 15:55:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The problem was that the font has an unusual cmap table combination and we ended up with a mac table that pointed to the wrong gid.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
